00:13:32.600 --> 00:13:36.090
What was c equals 0 and
a 100, those were the

00:13:36.090 --> 00:13:39.920
key points for c.

00:13:39.920 --> 00:13:48.310
f equals 32 and 212 were
they key points for f.

00:13:48.310 --> 00:13:50.780
This was on the graph, right?

00:13:50.780 --> 00:13:54.500
0 centigrade gives
32 Fahrenheit.

00:13:54.500 --> 00:13:56.850
100 centigrade matches 212.

00:13:56.850 --> 00:13:59.630
That's on the graph.

00:13:59.630 --> 00:14:03.967
And again, it's a
line in between.

00:14:03.967 --> 00:14:05.217
Hoo!

00:14:06.930 --> 00:14:09.310
My picture isn't so fantastic.

00:14:09.310 --> 00:14:12.110
That 212 really should be
higher, and that line should

00:14:12.110 --> 00:14:14.810
